# --- Personal LLM-wiki vault content (kept local, never shipped to the public repo) ---
# The maintainer dogfoods Memex on a private vault that lives in this repo. Its raw
# sources and the wiki pages generated from them (often derived from third-party
# material) stay on disk for local use but are NOT tracked. Only the small self-made
# sample below ships, so a fresh checkout still has something to ingest and render.
/raw/*
/wiki/*
/ingest-reports/*
# ...but DO ship the structure + the self-made sample:
!/raw/.gitkeep
!/raw/assets/
!/raw/getting-started.md
!/wiki/.gitkeep
!/wiki/index.md
!/wiki/log.md
!/wiki/memex.md
!/wiki/source-getting-started.md
!/ingest-reports/.gitkeep

# Node (stray npx artifacts — the app manages its own under app/)
node_modules/

# Project backups (export_project output)
projects/.backups/

# Planning / dev-status docs — keep local, not on GitHub
plans/
